WEBVTT


00:00:49.470 --> 00:00:52.950
[The Ferry Man: 10th Anniversary]

00:00:53.510 --> 00:00:56.040
[Episode 19]

00:01:07.150 --> 00:01:08.350
What a huge building.

00:01:08.480 --> 00:01:10.150
This is Blue Blood Tech.

00:01:10.680 --> 00:01:12.150
Don't you want to go in and take a look

00:01:12.150 --> 00:01:13.350
at a demon's company?

00:01:13.430 --> 00:01:14.760
How do we get in, though?

00:01:15.120 --> 00:01:16.070
I nearly forgot this:

00:01:16.070 --> 00:01:17.710
since we don't work here, we'll have to

00:01:17.710 --> 00:01:18.980
walk in while crouching down,

00:01:18.980 --> 00:01:20.310
so as not to be found out.

00:01:20.950 --> 00:01:21.940
Are you sure this will work?

00:01:21.940 --> 00:01:23.670
I am a night watchman. Trust me.

00:01:25.789 --> 00:01:26.320
Let's go.

00:01:35.560 --> 00:01:36.229
Zhao Hengzhi,

00:01:36.229 --> 00:01:37.490
what's wrong with you?

00:01:42.430 --> 00:01:42.920
Hello.

00:01:44.070 --> 00:01:45.039
Who are you?

00:01:45.479 --> 00:01:46.410
We're visitors.

00:01:46.950 --> 00:01:48.009
Any appointments?

00:01:48.229 --> 00:01:48.590
No.

00:01:50.400 --> 00:01:51.560
You're so pretty.

00:01:51.789 --> 00:01:52.520
Are you a fox,

00:01:52.680 --> 00:01:53.680
with three tails?

00:01:57.310 --> 00:01:58.840
You're fellow demons then.

00:01:59.200 --> 00:01:59.640
No.

00:02:00.510 --> 00:02:01.570
You are not demons.

00:02:01.710 --> 00:02:02.910
I am a night watchman.

00:02:03.280 --> 00:02:04.010
He is a human.

00:02:06.230 --> 00:02:07.310
We're not here to cause trouble.

00:02:07.310 --> 00:02:07.940
This company

00:02:07.940 --> 00:02:08.800
is legitimate.

00:02:08.910 --> 00:02:10.630
I just want a meeting with your boss.

00:02:10.630 --> 00:02:13.240
Perhaps he'll be interested
in cooperating with me.

00:02:13.240 --> 00:02:14.360
As you know, technology is advancing.

00:02:14.360 --> 00:02:16.060
Night watchmen also need to
keep abreast of the times.

00:02:16.060 --> 00:02:17.280
Please give him a call.

00:02:17.280 --> 00:02:18.280
By the way,

00:02:18.560 --> 00:02:19.960
you really are gorgeous.

00:02:21.310 --> 00:02:21.910
Fine then.

00:02:23.800 --> 00:02:24.800
A night watchman?

00:02:26.840 --> 00:02:28.510
Cooperation? What kind of cooperation?

00:02:28.510 --> 00:02:29.590
Let them come up here.

00:02:29.590 --> 00:02:30.000
Got it.

00:02:43.520 --> 00:02:44.150
Xu.

00:02:45.650 --> 00:02:46.520
Quickly bring your daughter

00:02:46.520 --> 00:02:47.850
to the Children's Park.

00:02:48.800 --> 00:02:50.130
Don't delay it anymore.

00:02:50.150 --> 00:02:51.190
She's already two years old.

00:02:51.190 --> 00:02:52.120
I... I know.

00:02:52.750 --> 00:02:54.810
My wife just feels reluctant to do so.

00:03:01.870 --> 00:03:03.930
Demons' children are little demons.

00:03:04.960 --> 00:03:05.960
They can't live

00:03:05.960 --> 00:03:07.020
in the human world.

00:03:07.300 --> 00:03:08.110
Your daughter won't have a future

00:03:08.110 --> 00:03:09.510
unless you send her here.

00:03:11.470 --> 00:03:13.470
It's not like I'm trying to harm you.

00:03:15.130 --> 00:03:16.120
You wouldn't be qualified for this

00:03:16.120 --> 00:03:18.050
if you weren't a veteran employee.

00:03:18.240 --> 00:03:18.630
I...

00:03:20.150 --> 00:03:22.210
I'll convince my wife as soon as I can.

00:03:22.240 --> 00:03:24.030
Do you know how to write it or not?

00:03:24.030 --> 00:03:24.800
Yes, I'll write it now.

00:03:24.800 --> 00:03:25.280
Hurry!

00:03:37.710 --> 00:03:39.190
That guy is a weasel demon.

00:03:42.430 --> 00:03:43.890
Why are there humans here?

00:03:43.960 --> 00:03:45.720
We never discriminate against humans.

00:03:45.720 --> 00:03:46.440
A quarter

00:03:46.470 --> 00:03:48.000
of the employees here are humans.

00:03:48.000 --> 00:03:48.960
As long as they're willing to work

00:03:48.960 --> 00:03:49.860
and have required skills,

00:03:49.860 --> 00:03:51.520
humans can certainly join us.

00:04:00.470 --> 00:04:02.080
You have quite a large space here.

00:04:02.080 --> 00:04:04.340
Haven't we reached the CEO's office yet?

00:04:04.520 --> 00:04:05.900
It's just around the corner.

00:04:05.900 --> 00:04:06.900
This way, please.

00:04:10.870 --> 00:04:12.530
Don't worry. See you at night.

00:04:15.800 --> 00:04:16.870
What's wrong with you lot?

00:04:16.870 --> 00:04:17.950
Is the company going to

00:04:17.950 --> 00:04:18.360
fall apart

00:04:18.360 --> 00:04:19.560
with Yan Yuzhen gone?

00:04:19.630 --> 00:04:20.430
If you have to,

00:04:20.480 --> 00:04:21.399
recruit someone on the street.

00:04:21.399 --> 00:04:22.040
I can see a lot of

00:04:22.040 --> 00:04:23.600
pretty young girls out there.

00:04:23.600 --> 00:04:24.800
If you can't find any,

00:04:24.800 --> 00:04:26.360
then hire some good-looking guys.

00:04:26.360 --> 00:04:28.190
We're running an MCN agency here.

00:04:28.190 --> 00:04:29.680
Streamers matter most to us.

00:04:29.680 --> 00:04:30.560
I'm keeping all of you

00:04:30.560 --> 00:04:31.430
on payroll for...

00:04:31.430 --> 00:04:32.430
for nothing.

00:04:33.000 --> 00:04:33.600
Director,

00:04:33.630 --> 00:04:34.560
are you alright?

00:04:35.000 --> 00:04:35.680
I'm fine.

00:04:35.900 --> 00:04:36.950
Would you like a rest?

00:04:36.950 --> 00:04:37.880
I'm a bit unwell.

00:04:38.360 --> 00:04:38.920
Director!

00:04:38.920 --> 00:04:39.290
What's going on?

00:04:39.290 --> 00:04:39.890
Director!

00:04:42.250 --> 00:04:43.850
Director, rinse your mouth.

00:04:46.680 --> 00:04:48.010
Why am I feeling so sick?

00:04:48.360 --> 00:04:49.430
Probably because of pregnancy.

00:04:49.430 --> 00:04:50.430
It's very normal.

00:04:55.310 --> 00:04:55.909
Director,

00:04:56.580 --> 00:04:58.110
is there a cut in your mouth?

00:05:06.190 --> 00:05:07.790
A tooth of mine just came out.

00:05:18.920 --> 00:05:20.510
Are you both night watchmen?

00:05:20.510 --> 00:05:21.190
Only I am.

00:05:22.900 --> 00:05:23.980
He is my best friend,

00:05:23.980 --> 00:05:25.110
named Xia Dongqing.

00:05:30.430 --> 00:05:31.830
This name

00:05:31.870 --> 00:05:33.390
sounds a bit familiar.

00:05:34.040 --> 00:05:35.800
Please don't get so close to me.

00:05:36.390 --> 00:05:37.920
I can smell your fox stench.

00:05:42.270 --> 00:05:43.510
Chi You's vessel

00:05:44.850 --> 00:05:45.920
has always been with

00:05:45.920 --> 00:05:46.580
a ferry man.

00:05:46.950 --> 00:05:48.080
He's the guy, right?

00:05:48.560 --> 00:05:49.290
Yes, it's me.

00:05:49.750 --> 00:05:50.270
Neither of you

00:05:50.270 --> 00:05:51.470
are ordinary people.

00:05:52.060 --> 00:05:52.560
I'd like to hear

00:05:52.560 --> 00:05:53.960
what kind of cooperation

00:05:55.000 --> 00:05:56.330
you're seeking with me.

00:05:56.440 --> 00:05:57.130
As you know,

00:05:57.159 --> 00:05:59.490
night watchmen always rely on talismans.

00:05:59.870 --> 00:06:01.130
It's their tradition.

00:06:02.120 --> 00:06:03.240
Can you help us

00:06:03.560 --> 00:06:05.190
upgrade the method?

00:06:05.310 --> 00:06:06.770
I just haven't figured out

00:06:06.870 --> 00:06:08.130
the means to resort to.

00:06:08.160 --> 00:06:09.120
Night Watchman,

00:06:10.140 --> 00:06:11.390
I can encode your talismans

00:06:11.390 --> 00:06:12.800
into your genes.

00:06:13.630 --> 00:06:14.680
On different occasions,

00:06:14.680 --> 00:06:15.330
your body will

00:06:15.330 --> 00:06:16.920
react accordingly on its own.

00:06:16.920 --> 00:06:17.520
Of course,

00:06:17.830 --> 00:06:19.310
I need you to give me

00:06:19.750 --> 00:06:20.750
all the talismans

00:06:20.920 --> 00:06:23.250
that night watchmen use, including those

00:06:23.260 --> 00:06:24.560
for combat, cultivation,

00:06:24.560 --> 00:06:25.620
and even survival.

00:06:26.160 --> 00:06:27.020
Do you trust me?

00:06:29.720 --> 00:06:31.950
It's just that there are too many of them.

00:06:31.950 --> 00:06:32.830
Giving you all the talismans

00:06:32.830 --> 00:06:34.140
won't necessarily be a bad thing.

00:06:34.140 --> 00:06:35.330
This way, you can create

00:06:35.330 --> 00:06:36.860
many, many night watchmen.

00:06:37.310 --> 00:06:37.950
However,

00:06:37.970 --> 00:06:39.600
before we actually cooperate,

00:06:39.600 --> 00:06:40.950
could you please tell me

00:06:41.240 --> 00:06:43.190
what your core technology is?

00:06:43.510 --> 00:06:45.510
The dimensional integration system.

00:06:45.510 --> 00:06:46.840
But it's of no use to you.

00:06:47.180 --> 00:06:47.970
So you mean

00:06:48.000 --> 00:06:49.390
the system that brings

00:06:49.409 --> 00:06:50.720
game characters to reality.

00:06:50.720 --> 00:06:51.980
It's very impressive.

00:06:52.630 --> 00:06:54.430
How did you manage to develop it?

00:07:00.480 --> 00:07:01.940
The Avatamsaka Sutra says

00:07:03.270 --> 00:07:05.330
everything is a creation of the mind.

00:07:07.160 --> 00:07:08.160
And the mind

00:07:08.830 --> 00:07:10.880
is the source of the entire world.

00:07:11.390 --> 00:07:14.600
The world is made of trillions of wishes,

00:07:14.920 --> 00:07:16.650
and interwoven with thoughts.

00:07:16.800 --> 00:07:18.870
It actually resembles
some kind of algorithm.

00:07:18.870 --> 00:07:20.560
Through algorithms and data,

00:07:20.600 --> 00:07:22.200
we can build a virtual world,

00:07:22.290 --> 00:07:23.680
which is just like a concrete

00:07:23.680 --> 00:07:25.020
manifestation of the mind.

00:07:25.020 --> 00:07:25.900
Since the world

00:07:25.930 --> 00:07:27.330
is a creation of the mind,

00:07:27.720 --> 00:07:29.510
a point of intersection
can certainly be found to merge

00:07:29.510 --> 00:07:30.970
reality with virtuality.

00:07:32.110 --> 00:07:33.360
Where is that point?

00:07:34.590 --> 00:07:35.720
Do you know about AI?

00:07:37.090 --> 00:07:38.120
I suppose everyone knows

00:07:38.120 --> 00:07:39.040
about AI now.

00:07:39.409 --> 00:07:40.560
The AI tools on your phone

00:07:40.560 --> 00:07:42.560
can't possibly tell you the answer.

00:07:42.800 --> 00:07:44.040
To run such massive

00:07:44.070 --> 00:07:45.400
and complex algorithms

00:07:45.600 --> 00:07:46.190
obviously requires

00:07:46.190 --> 00:07:47.920
a tremendous amount of energy.

00:07:54.270 --> 00:07:55.040
Do you...

00:07:55.710 --> 00:07:56.970
know who Yan Yuzhen is?

00:08:00.090 --> 00:08:01.390
Are you here to pry for information?

00:08:01.390 --> 00:08:02.480
I'm just asking.

00:08:03.560 --> 00:08:06.290
You've been asking me questions
the entire time.

00:08:06.750 --> 00:08:08.680
I also have a few questions for you.

00:08:09.800 --> 00:08:11.130
What do you want to know?

00:08:14.500 --> 00:08:16.300
Are you really a night watchman?

00:08:20.150 --> 00:08:21.750
Zhao Hengzhi, there are many bubbles.

00:08:21.750 --> 00:08:23.480
Beware of the fox's illusions!

00:08:27.430 --> 00:08:29.310
Night Watchman, Xia Dongqing,

00:08:30.000 --> 00:08:31.730
show me what you're capable of.

00:08:39.909 --> 00:08:41.600
A quick-change performance, huh?

00:08:41.600 --> 00:08:42.120
First,

00:08:42.270 --> 00:08:43.400
you are very pretty.

00:08:43.510 --> 00:08:44.000
Second,

00:08:44.390 --> 00:08:45.670
I'd hate to hit a woman.

00:09:46.440 --> 00:09:47.390
Dongqing!

00:10:05.390 --> 00:10:06.190
Zhao Hengzhi!

00:10:06.270 --> 00:10:07.000
Are you okay?

00:10:10.150 --> 00:10:10.550
You...

00:10:12.600 --> 00:10:13.460
I didn't expect

00:10:14.080 --> 00:10:15.600
Situ Fei's blood to be blue.

00:10:15.600 --> 00:10:16.860
He's a demon after all.

00:10:16.910 --> 00:10:19.040
His company is called Blue Blood Tech.

00:10:19.520 --> 00:10:20.920
Then I must go wash up now.

00:10:20.930 --> 00:10:22.080
My skin is not great to begin with.

00:10:22.080 --> 00:10:23.740
It can't take any more damage.

00:10:26.240 --> 00:10:27.440
I remember in nature,

00:10:28.000 --> 00:10:29.800
only octopuses have blue blood.

00:10:30.800 --> 00:10:32.530
Is there still blood on my face?

00:10:32.790 --> 00:10:34.510
Octopus, cuttlefish, squid...

00:10:34.510 --> 00:10:35.480
I can't tell them apart.

00:10:35.480 --> 00:10:36.880
I think your face is clean now.

00:10:36.880 --> 00:10:37.480
I'll wash it again later.

00:10:37.480 --> 00:10:37.940
Hold on!

00:10:39.080 --> 00:10:39.940
Why? What's up?

00:10:40.080 --> 00:10:40.680
Your neck.

00:10:46.480 --> 00:10:48.030
Why is there still blood on me?

00:10:48.030 --> 00:10:49.390
I'll take you for a bath later.

00:10:49.390 --> 00:10:49.910
Where?

00:10:51.960 --> 00:10:52.760
Zhao Hengzhi.

00:10:53.150 --> 00:10:54.280
Today is a lucky day.

00:10:54.630 --> 00:10:55.240
Lucky day?

00:10:55.360 --> 00:10:56.390
What lucky day?

00:10:58.240 --> 00:10:59.510
It's not my lucky day,

00:11:01.270 --> 00:11:02.790
but Xu's.

00:11:03.550 --> 00:11:04.200
Dongqing.

00:11:04.440 --> 00:11:06.130
Honey, you finally answered the phone.

00:11:06.130 --> 00:11:06.960
Where did you go?

00:11:06.960 --> 00:11:08.000
You weren't at the shop.

00:11:08.000 --> 00:11:09.060
Have you gone home?

00:11:09.540 --> 00:11:10.740
I'm already off work.

00:11:11.320 --> 00:11:12.550
But I have some things

00:11:12.630 --> 00:11:13.560
to deal with now.

00:11:14.030 --> 00:11:15.230
Don't worry about me.

00:11:16.060 --> 00:11:17.060
I'm not worried.

00:11:17.340 --> 00:11:18.500
I'm just asking.

00:11:19.360 --> 00:11:20.820
You are a Heavenly Maiden.

00:11:20.850 --> 00:11:22.310
Who dares to mess with you?

00:11:22.840 --> 00:11:25.100
I'll come home once I finish my business.

00:11:28.550 --> 00:11:29.440
Here comes a guest.

00:11:29.440 --> 00:11:30.240
I'll hang up then.

00:11:30.240 --> 00:11:31.600
Talk to you later at home tonight.

00:11:31.600 --> 00:11:32.080
Xu.

00:11:42.150 --> 00:11:43.550
We've got a little guest.

00:11:45.510 --> 00:11:47.030
This is my wife, Wanping.

00:11:48.960 --> 00:11:50.160
This is our daughter,

00:11:50.360 --> 00:11:51.000
Niuniu.

00:11:53.030 --> 00:11:53.700
Niuniu,

00:11:54.240 --> 00:11:55.150
You are so adorable.

00:11:55.150 --> 00:11:56.000
How old are you?

00:11:56.000 --> 00:11:56.940
I'm two years old.

00:11:56.940 --> 00:11:58.000
Two years old, huh?

00:11:59.080 --> 00:12:00.480
Soon I'll be a father too.

00:12:01.840 --> 00:12:02.390
How about

00:12:02.490 --> 00:12:03.550
I introduce a little friend

00:12:03.550 --> 00:12:05.010
for you to play with later?

00:12:06.510 --> 00:12:07.630
Take a seat, all of you.

00:12:07.630 --> 00:12:09.360
I'll go fix some drinks for you.

00:12:13.910 --> 00:12:15.000
Nothing's wrong.

00:12:15.870 --> 00:12:16.790
But

00:12:17.030 --> 00:12:18.030
why would a tooth of mine

00:12:18.030 --> 00:12:19.290
fall out for no reason?

00:12:19.790 --> 00:12:21.120
That was a wisdom tooth.

00:12:21.270 --> 00:12:22.140
You're pregnant.

00:12:22.140 --> 00:12:23.440
Pregnancy could lead to

00:12:23.440 --> 00:12:24.700
unusual body changes.

00:12:24.960 --> 00:12:26.320
What do these unusual body changes

00:12:26.320 --> 00:12:27.650
have to do with my teeth?

00:12:27.840 --> 00:12:29.630
The human body is very complex.

00:12:29.910 --> 00:12:31.480
Maybe your pregnancy

00:12:31.910 --> 00:12:33.110
and lack of nutrition

00:12:33.230 --> 00:12:34.640
caused your body to think

00:12:34.670 --> 00:12:36.870
the entire system was quickly declining

00:12:36.870 --> 00:12:38.080
and that you were getting old,

00:12:38.080 --> 00:12:39.320
so bone resorption happened.

00:12:39.320 --> 00:12:40.480
Things like wisdom teeth

00:12:40.480 --> 00:12:41.840
would naturally fall out.

00:12:41.840 --> 00:12:42.770
I'm getting old?

00:12:42.910 --> 00:12:43.550
Look,

00:12:44.010 --> 00:12:45.090
you even have a few

00:12:45.120 --> 00:12:45.980
grey hairs now.

00:12:46.320 --> 00:12:47.320
Grey hairs?

00:12:47.810 --> 00:12:49.210
You just lack nutrition.

00:12:49.510 --> 00:12:50.860
What you lost was a mere wisdom tooth.

00:12:50.860 --> 00:12:51.600
Many young girls would

00:12:51.600 --> 00:12:53.320
specifically come
to have their wisdom teeth pulled.

00:12:53.320 --> 00:12:55.380
Try taking in more nutritional food.

00:12:55.390 --> 00:12:56.250
Pregnant women

00:12:56.270 --> 00:12:57.870
need sufficient nutrition.

00:12:59.600 --> 00:13:00.750
I have

00:13:01.160 --> 00:13:02.640
an ordinary woman's body,

00:13:02.670 --> 00:13:03.150
right?

00:13:03.720 --> 00:13:04.580
Yes, ordinary.

00:13:04.910 --> 00:13:06.750
To be accurate,
you have a regular woman's body.

00:13:06.750 --> 00:13:07.720
No need to worry.

00:13:07.870 --> 00:13:08.440
Pregnancy

00:13:08.440 --> 00:13:09.790
is a difficult journey for women.

00:13:09.790 --> 00:13:12.450
You'll notice
all sorts of unusual conditions.

00:13:21.440 --> 00:13:22.120
Doctor.

00:13:22.670 --> 00:13:23.840
The baby in my womb

00:13:24.600 --> 00:13:25.720
just kicked me.

00:13:27.510 --> 00:13:28.630
You are a human?

00:13:30.030 --> 00:13:31.270
Then you two...

00:13:32.470 --> 00:13:33.840
When Wanping met me,

00:13:34.600 --> 00:13:35.390
she already knew

00:13:35.390 --> 00:13:36.240
I'm a demon.

00:13:37.360 --> 00:13:38.210
I used to work

00:13:38.240 --> 00:13:39.550
at Blue Blood Tech too.

00:13:39.980 --> 00:13:41.270
That's where I met Xu.

00:13:41.750 --> 00:13:43.010
I think he's very nice.

00:13:43.510 --> 00:13:44.570
He's a good person—

00:13:44.720 --> 00:13:45.870
a good demon, to be exact.

00:13:45.870 --> 00:13:47.390
All I care about is his good character

00:13:47.390 --> 00:13:48.850
and that he treats me well.

00:13:49.750 --> 00:13:51.550
No matter Xu is a demon or a human,

00:13:52.080 --> 00:13:53.140
I just want to spend

00:13:53.320 --> 00:13:54.850
the rest of my life with him.

00:13:57.050 --> 00:13:58.440
Did you resign?

00:13:58.600 --> 00:13:59.080
Yes,

00:13:59.440 --> 00:14:00.630
before I married Xu.

00:14:00.890 --> 00:14:01.600
Getting married

00:14:01.600 --> 00:14:03.230
while we were working in the same office

00:14:03.230 --> 00:14:04.550
wasn't a good idea after all.

00:14:04.550 --> 00:14:05.080
Xu,

00:14:05.750 --> 00:14:07.350
employees of Blue Blood Tech

00:14:07.550 --> 00:14:09.270
aren't allowed to quit, are they?

00:14:09.270 --> 00:14:10.600
Humans are exceptions.

00:14:11.480 --> 00:14:12.610
Sounds about right.

00:14:13.100 --> 00:14:15.240
Due to humans' limited energy

00:14:15.270 --> 00:14:16.470
and short lifespans,

00:14:16.960 --> 00:14:17.870
they can't commit to

00:14:17.870 --> 00:14:19.730
long-term high-intensity work.

00:14:20.870 --> 00:14:22.000
Demon bosses mainly

00:14:22.080 --> 00:14:23.540
exploit demon employees.

00:14:23.630 --> 00:14:24.080
Yes.

00:14:25.630 --> 00:14:26.630
Niuniu, drink this.

00:14:26.630 --> 00:14:27.200
It's sweet.

00:14:27.200 --> 00:14:28.600
Thank you, uncle.

00:14:29.200 --> 00:14:29.870
Good girl.

00:14:31.440 --> 00:14:32.030
Xu.

00:14:32.840 --> 00:14:33.840
Well,

00:14:34.510 --> 00:14:35.910
your child...

00:14:36.840 --> 00:14:37.840
Niuniu is a hybrid

00:14:37.960 --> 00:14:39.320
of a human and a demon.

00:14:39.510 --> 00:14:40.770
So she's a half-demon.

00:14:42.960 --> 00:14:44.360
Mom, drink this.

00:14:45.600 --> 00:14:46.080
Niuniu,

00:14:46.600 --> 00:14:47.960
I've told you many times not to

00:14:47.960 --> 00:14:48.750
recklessly move things around

00:14:48.750 --> 00:14:49.950
in others' presence.

00:14:52.240 --> 00:14:54.870
She's basically a little demon.

00:14:57.600 --> 00:14:59.130
It took me hundreds of years

00:15:00.000 --> 00:15:01.460
to finally build a family.

00:15:03.080 --> 00:15:03.720
So,

00:15:04.510 --> 00:15:06.840
my family is the most precious thing
to me.

00:15:07.440 --> 00:15:08.900
I want to leave the company

00:15:09.630 --> 00:15:10.870
and be with my wife.

00:15:12.150 --> 00:15:13.150
I hope to watch Niuniu

00:15:13.150 --> 00:15:14.550
grow up little by little.

00:15:15.360 --> 00:15:16.030
That's why

00:15:16.750 --> 00:15:17.950
I came to you for help.

00:15:18.670 --> 00:15:19.870
You want me to help you

00:15:20.480 --> 00:15:21.540
leave the company?

00:15:22.480 --> 00:15:23.240
Mr. Zhao,

00:15:24.360 --> 00:15:25.630
do you have any solutions?

00:15:25.630 --> 00:15:26.960
If Xu tries to run away,

00:15:27.670 --> 00:15:28.630
the employee badge on him

00:15:28.630 --> 00:15:29.600
will kill him.

00:15:30.510 --> 00:15:31.080
Xu,

00:15:31.910 --> 00:15:32.910
can you show me that badge

00:15:32.910 --> 00:15:34.040
on your chest again?

00:15:43.270 --> 00:15:44.530
Shall we take a gamble?

00:15:46.280 --> 00:15:47.450
Your boss is a demon,

00:15:47.480 --> 00:15:47.880
right?

00:15:48.840 --> 00:15:50.040
Since ancient times,

00:15:50.220 --> 00:15:51.720
demons have controlled other demons

00:15:51.720 --> 00:15:53.030
by forming blood pacts.

00:15:53.030 --> 00:15:54.950
The former use their blood
to plant something

00:15:54.950 --> 00:15:56.350
into the latter's bodies

00:15:56.360 --> 00:15:57.550
to gain lifelong control.

00:15:57.550 --> 00:15:58.910
Only the former's blood

00:15:59.840 --> 00:16:01.240
can break the blood pacts.

00:16:01.240 --> 00:16:02.120
That is to say,

00:16:02.630 --> 00:16:04.360
we need to get your boss's blood.

00:16:04.360 --> 00:16:05.420
We already have it.

00:16:09.480 --> 00:16:10.670
This bit on here

00:16:11.150 --> 00:16:12.350
is Xu's boss's blood.

00:16:12.670 --> 00:16:14.130
Your boss's blood is blue.

00:16:15.120 --> 00:16:15.670
Xu,

00:16:16.390 --> 00:16:17.360
maybe today

00:16:18.480 --> 00:16:19.570
is your lucky day.

00:16:20.960 --> 00:16:22.220
Will you take a gamble?

00:16:22.270 --> 00:16:24.070
The employee badge on your chest

00:16:24.270 --> 00:16:25.200
is a blood pact.

00:16:28.790 --> 00:16:29.850
I'll take a gamble.

00:16:30.360 --> 00:16:31.020
As you said,

00:16:31.870 --> 00:16:33.080
today is my lucky day.